body:
The last two normal games i got into, champ select freezes at random times. first time was halfway through picking champs, second time it was the last ban. After leagues hasn't been responding for 10 minutes i force close, then get timers. the second time my entire team left before me (I could see in the chat logs that everyone left) and i still get a 15 minute ban.  I know 15 minutes isn't bad, i have other stuff i can do for now, but if it keeps happening i don't want to deal with longer bans. 

Ranked games haven't had this problem so far for me. but I don't want to try new builds or champs in ranked.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
